Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.53,0:00:46.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My pre-emptive strike failed.\NThat makes things difficult.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.72,0:00:52.37,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got two grenades left.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.37,0:00:55.41,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to get as close as possible, take out its legs.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.41,0:00:59.71,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then aim for the topside armor\Nand knock it out of commission.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.38,0:01:28.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't waste ammo, I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.82,0:01:37.59,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Standard operating protocol when faced\Nwith an enemy of unknown firepower.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.59,0:01:39.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Then resumes suppressive fire...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.70,0:01:40.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Knew it!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.88,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One... two... three!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit... my ears...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.94,0:02:23.41,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Need to assess the situation!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.22,0:02:30.93,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It takes thirty seconds to reload.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.93,0:02:32.71,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Won't be long before it fires again!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.78,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A fracture?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.78,0:02:38.47,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye, a leg for a leg, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.31,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you do such a stupid thing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.99,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Mr. Customer.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.54,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I told you to stay put until I got back!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.78,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The unregistered machine appeared\Nto be in a rampant state.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.78,0:05:13.96,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A force-stop signal was sent, but was ignored.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.96,0:05:17.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The receiver may have been out of order,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.29,0:05:21.80,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,so an emergency physical shutdown\Nwas attempted, and failed.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.04,0:05:26.80,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The rampant machine appears\Nto have ceased functioning.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.44,0:05:31.07,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please step away from the rampant machine
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.07,0:05:34.74,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,and report this incident to a nearby\Npolice station or support center.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.74,0:05:39.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,My sincerest apologies for\Nviolating a critical directive.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.27,0:05:44.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,However, there was an older promise I had to keep.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.19,0:05:49.28,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I must not knowingly allow\Nany human being to come to harm.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.72,0:05:54.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Keeping this promise is the pride of us robots.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.31,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Customer,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.31,0:05:58.69,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,are you injured?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.17,0:06:04.57,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That is most relieving to hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.65,0:06:09.96,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I apologize on his behalf.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.96,0:06:13.31,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I believe he may have malfunctioned, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.70,0:06:20.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We robots were created\Nfor the happiness of humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.87,0:06:25.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he never wanted to act with such violence.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.45,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.71,0:06:34.08,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Because I, too, am slightly malfunctional.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.20,0:06:49.22,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The emergency batteries will deplete\Nin approximately 600 seconds.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Because the backup batteries are depleted,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.92,0:06:56.44,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I will be unable to boot after this.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.44,0:06:59.41,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I am sending a maintenance call,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.41,0:07:01.10,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,but it is not being acknowledged.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.98,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I feel somewhat abandoned.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You don't need to call anyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.77,0:07:07.99,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll save you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.23,0:07:11.95,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll fix you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.56,0:07:17.95,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,My sincerest apologies for my disorderly state.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.95,0:07:20.50,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please do not worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.48,0:07:24.04,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Since I am a robot,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.64,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I do not feel pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.56,0:07:30.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I can be repaired,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.90,0:07:35.01,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,or transferred to a whole new body.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.88,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There are no longer any engineers\Nthat can repair you...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.07,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Any bodies to replace yours...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.18,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Or any humans that need you...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Not in this world...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.19,0:07:53.69,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please, if you maintain that facial expression,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.21,0:07:55.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I will be most worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.41,0:07:59.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I am a robot.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.39,0:08:03.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,My customers' smiles are most important to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.94,0:08:06.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I remember every single one of them.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.14,0:08:11.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,As a robot, I am good at remembering things.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.98,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I am Hoshino Yumemi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.98,0:08:20.58,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for this wonderful name.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.03,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I will be sure to do my best.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.55,0:08:30.53,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Yumemi!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.53,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yumemi, thank you for the pretty stars.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.45,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll bring all of my friends next time,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.54,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,so stay well!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.29,0:08:43.71,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll visit with my wife on our anniversary.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.80,0:08:50.64,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The starry sky was as beautiful\Nas it was when I was younger.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.15,0:08:55.22,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I hope to visit you again next year.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.43,0:09:00.03,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot about the stars,\Nand I had a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.03,0:09:04.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,For my summer science project,\NI'll write about you, Yumemi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.59,0:09:09.78,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Um, it was super pretty, and really moving!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so gonna come again!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.49,0:09:15.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I love you, Yumemi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.51,0:09:17.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.51,0:09:20.99,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We eagerly await your return.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.92,0:09:27.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yumemi, we um...\Nneed to go on a trip for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.73,0:09:31.20,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A trip? That sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.71,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yumemi...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.71,0:09:39.06,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Could you please wait for us here until we return?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.06,0:09:43.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, understood. When will you be returning?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.17,0:09:51.04,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,W-We're not really sure yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.04,0:09:56.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But we'll be back for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.33,0:09:59.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,When that happens,\Nlet's work together again, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Yumemi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Manager.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.50,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Yumemi...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.48,0:10:12.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,To leave you out here, all alone...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.09,0:10:15.59,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please do not worry about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.59,0:10:20.04,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I will be waiting here for you with\NMiss Jena for as long as you need.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.86,0:10:28.77,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please leave matters in my hands,\Nand enjoy your trip.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.04,0:10:36.49,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That was from 29 years and 71 days ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.97,0:10:44.67,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,44 years and 138 days have passed since\Nour first projection at the planetarium.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.16,0:10:52.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Until you came, Mr. Customer,\Ntime after time I wondered...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.31,0:10:59.13,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,When would Mr. Manager and\Nthe other staff members return?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.98,0:11:03.89,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,When would our next customer arrive?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.58,0:11:08.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I always found myself reaching\Nthe same conclusion—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.73,0:11:13.81,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,that the humans would never return again.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.90,0:11:18.10,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But that was impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.10,0:11:22.74,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That is why I thought I must\Nhave been malfunctioning.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.74,0:11:27.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I ran my self-diagnostic program to locate the error.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.94,0:11:32.83,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,However, no error could be found.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.25,0:11:39.57,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Therefore, I concluded that there must be an\Nunknown bug within the self-diagnostic program.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.06,0:11:43.54,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,When you arrived, Mr. Customer,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.54,0:11:47.04,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I was overjoyed.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It seemed I was wrong after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.46,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The customers had not forgotten about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.46,0:12:01.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That is what I thought, and it made me very happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.18,0:12:06.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But again, I was wrong about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.62,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There was nothing wrong with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.96,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong was...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.35,0:12:19.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Why is the world all wrong...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.54,0:12:25.77,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The emergency batteries will deplete
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.86,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,in approximately 150 seconds.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.43,0:12:32.80,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Because the backup batteries are depleted,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.80,0:12:36.52,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I will be unable to boot after this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.14,0:12:41.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I can record one more message.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.06,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Customer,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.95,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,to commemorate your visit to our planetarium,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.53,0:12:51.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,please record a message with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.85,0:12:57.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Listen closely.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.52,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.19,0:13:07.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I came to get you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.29,0:13:09.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Could you clarify?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.75,0:13:14.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,On the other side of that wall\Nis a new workplace for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.57,0:13:19.42,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Your projector partner, your coworkers,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.57,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,they're all waiting for you there.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.89,0:13:25.57,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There's also a venue full of customers,\Nall waiting for you too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.79,0:13:29.26,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone's eagerly waiting for your commentary.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's your new workplace, starting today.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.77,0:13:34.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You can work there
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.34,0:13:39.08,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,for as long as you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.46,0:13:44.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's just like Heaven, is it not?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.45,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.09,0:13:49.78,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.07,0:13:57.10,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I finally understood who you are, Mr. Customer.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.04,0:14:03.18,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Customer, will you hear my wish?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, what is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.36,0:14:09.38,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Behind my ear receiver
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.38,0:14:12.49,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,is a memory card slot.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.00,0:14:18.84,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,All of my memories are stored there.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.41,0:14:24.22,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Each and every one is precious to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.22,0:14:29.59,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you to deliver it to my new workplace?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.24,0:14:34.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you can provide me with a new body,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.76,0:14:38.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I can start working on that very day.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.02,0:14:49.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I can continue working for people\Nfor as long as I am allowed.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.44,0:14:55.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,So, to tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.13,0:15:02.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I do not need a heaven.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.49,0:15:13.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,However, if I must go to Heaven,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.91,0:15:18.06,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,please, God,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.13,0:15:22.82,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,do not divide Heaven in two.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.41,0:15:30.07,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please do not divide robots and humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.79,0:15:39.95,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I would very much like to work\Nfor humans... forever and ever...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.95,0:15:43.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I understand. I will do as you wish.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.40,0:15:50.03,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you... very much...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.81,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I am overjoyed.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Customer?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Customer?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.95,0:16:07.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.39,0:16:10.20,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.20,0:16:15.28,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It seems I am indeed\Nmalfunctioning slightly, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.49,0:16:20.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I am an Economy Edition model,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.95,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I lack the capability to shed tears.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.47,0:16:29.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,However, if I did have that functionality,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.25,0:16:34.37,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I believe I would most likely be crying now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.05,0:16:40.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I believe the tears would never stop.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.07,0:16:46.02,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But I am very happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.61,0:16:52.45,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I am filled with a joyous feeling.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.52,0:16:58.03,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,So... why?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.02,0:17:02.89,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what my new workplace will be like?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.90,0:17:09.07,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I must be in top condition,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.89,0:17:16.55,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,so that I can welcome my guests\Nwhenever they arrive.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.06,0:17:21.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come to the planetarium?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.49,0:17:32.42,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The beautiful twinkling
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.15,0:17:36.13,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,of eternity...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.06,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'd better get going...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.22,0:23:45.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you alive?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.14,0:23:50.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.29,0:23:51.66,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You a Junker too?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.23,0:23:56.41,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No... I'm...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.41,0:24:03.69,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,a starteller.
